blue-wattled crow
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number: 2
Definition:The two spp. also attract the occas. names <i>C. wilsoni</i>, blue (-wattled), North Island crow; <i>C. cinerea, </i>orange-wattled, South Island, (occas. early) yellow-wattled crow.


